     <h1> About this Project </h1>

 	 <h2> WHAT </h2>
 	   <p> TodaywasGreat.com is a site where any individual can share something about their day that made it great.  
 	   </p>
     <h2> WHY </h2>
       <p>The simple act of selecting a great moment from the day actually brings out greatness.  It allows for a more positive day-to-day perspective.  Why share it?  Happiness is contagious and inspired people inspire people.  It's a small step in making the world a better place. 
 	   </p>
     <h2> WHO</h2>
       <p>This site was started by a world traveler/mom/engineer by the name of Nina in 2011, but this site belongs to everyone.  Whether you tend to be an optimist, a pessimist, or somewhere in between, we all have a lot to gain from focusing on the positive parts of our days.
